snippet.title: Brothers in Hell - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
After you die, Death gives you the chance to come back to the world of the living to fulfill your deepest desire. Take the chance. Get back on your feet, and claim your revenge in this stealth action-adventure game available on PC on November 3rd
